        <Parent_String>misstruck coins [300206583], coins by form or technique [300191471], coins (money) [300037222], money by form [300264712], money (objects) [300037316], exchange media (objects) [300387350], Exchange Media (hierarchy name) [300037221], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
